{"tid":1101623,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"好人好者 睇乜柒嘢中超呀","createTime":"2019-04-11T07:11:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-11T11:53:40.000Z","uid":219590,"like":22,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"cc77fa0e01789536eff67c7acfcd074c518fa0b1","tid":1101623,"uid":219590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T07:11:58.000Z","msg":"是咁的，剛剛小弟同一個新黎HR去食飯。咁男人話題一向都係打機，炒股，睇波，女人。咁我就問吓佢有無咩特別鍾意睇既運動，果然不出我所料，佢話鍾意睇足球。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁我就問吓佢有無睇尋晚曼對巴嗰場波咯。佢竟然回答我：仲有人睇歐冠架咩，我同我班friend個個月都翻大陸去睇中超，好波過班歐洲佬好多，下次要唔要一齊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n哇，我屌。我好大聲對住佢講，乜柒嘢中超呀？你個腦係唔係裝屎架。你同你班friend on9好啦，唔好拉埋我落水呀。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有！係呀，係講緊你呀，今日新黎姓王既HR，我就係唔妥鳩你，知道你有睇連登，請你唔好再走過黎我個工作位置度扮friend。我一向對鍾意支那文化既人無興趣。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28629fde8bc18456bfe03af488f8060b346e77fd","tid":1101623,"uid":50658,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T07:17:12.000Z","msg":"呢個世界總有人鐘意睇賽狗"},{"pid":"cabfb160266feaeb0fc7b27bc4dbff5fa3f7e882","tid":1101623,"uid":5649,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T07:18:12.000Z","msg":"首先我唔針對中國，但中超好波過班歐洲佬？<br />\n佢係咪戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c143d056c551cb94214f8f8bb9e2bf34f405c6c2","tid":1101623,"uid":219590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28629fde8bc18456bfe03af488f8060b346e77fd","tid":1101623,"uid":50658,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T07:17:12.000Z","msg":"呢個世界總有人鐘意睇賽狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T07:18:56.000Z","msg":"睇法甲，荷甲都唔會睇中超啦吓哇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港人係唔係翻大陸翻到short q左"},{"pid":"fdbd8f5e8f4a8b7adab59e3a91524a15abbfb49c","tid":1101623,"uid":202348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cabfb160266feaeb0f